  \begin {tikzpicture}
    \draw  (0,0) -- (1,0) node[midway, below] {$p$} -- (1,1) node[midway, right] {$y$}
    -- (0,1) node[midway, above] {$q$} -- (0,0) node[midway, left] {$x$};
  \end {tikzpicture}.



We say p and q are path homotopic, written p\simeq _p q; this is an
equivalence relation.

